item.title: OverloadX 317 i need help
item.dc:creator: @crazyfazespy crazyfazespy
item.description:
@crazyfazespy wrote:

src\server\world
ObjectManager Class
Search for: public void loadCustomSpawns
And you will see like example

		c.getPA().checkObjectSpawn(6165, 3084, 3490, 1, 10);//clothes stall

6165 is object id 3084 cordx 3490 cordy 1 objectface 10(im not sure)
So to remove objects like bank boths etc…
you have to copy that code

c.getPA().checkObjectSpawn(6163, 3084, 3488, 1, 10);//bakery stall

And just make it look like

c.getPA().checkObjectSpawn(-1, objectcordx, objectcordy, 1, 10)

You can check ur cords by typing ::mypos
